<div class="content-section bisect">
  <div class="content-center">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Spark</h1>
    </div>
	    <div class="header">
      <h2>What should a Spark be?</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="p-right">
      An easy, simple, good deed that your friend will enjoy doing.
    </p>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>What is a Spark?</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="p-right">
      A good deed you design specifically for a friend to complete.
    </p>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Who gives a Spark?</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="p-right">
      Anyone who would like to help SPARK LOVE in the community.
    </p>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Why give a Spark?</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="p-right">
      Encourages others to promote positive actions and strengthens relationships.
    </p>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>How to give a spark?</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="p-right">
      Mail it, leave it in a door, on a desk, on their car anywhere any place you are 100% certain they will see it
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="content-section bisect">
  <div class="content-center">
    <h2 class="content-title">Spark Heroes</h2>
      <p class="p-right">
      Spark Heroes highlights <span class="wildFire">WILD FIRE</span> members that have went above and beyond to Spark Love in their local community.  
      </p>
        <p class="p-right quote">
          "Service which is rendered without joy helps neither the servant nor the served. But all other pleasures and possessions pale into nothingness before service which is rendered in a spirit of joy." 
        </p>
        <p class="p-right">
           -Mahatma Gandhi
        </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-section bisect">
  <div class="content-left">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Brittany Billings</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="p-right">
      Spark Hope
    </p>
    <p class="p-right quote">
     "I received a spark from Ashley Walke to make a meal for someone who needs it. Living downtown, I've had the opportunity to be exposed to many homeless individuals. I was happy about receiving this specific spark so I enjoyed planning the meals. I prepared and packed up a total of 8 meals and delivered them to 6 people who I thought would be most in need. It was chilly outside and many of the people I delivered meals to were hiding under layers of blankets trying to keep warm. It was a great feeling to be able to brighten their day and see the smiles that the spark ignited. Opportunities such as these are what Wildfire means to me. I am grateful for the extra push of inspiration that brought something thoughtful and meaningful to those who need it the most." 
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="content-right">
    <%= image_tag("Sparks/BrittanyBillingsSparkHope.jpg", :alt => "Spark Hope", :class => "eventImg") %>
  </div>
</div>

