    </p>
    <p class="p-right quote">
     "My spark was to play an entire of basketball without shooting at the basket. Instead I was to distribute the basketball cunningly to my teammates while enthusiastically encouraging them on. During the game, passing the ball to a teammate who scored and high-fiving them afterwards became more rewarding than any shot I could have taken. This spark brought out selflessness, team play, and sportsmanship." 
    </p>
